    body: [
      'Under California Civil Code Section 1789.3, California users are entitled to the following consumer rights notice: The Site is provided by Learning Source, LLC, 1701 Directors Blvd, Suite 800, Austin, TX 78744. If you have a question or complaint regarding the Site, please contact us at info@neurosagehub.com or (855) 960-7220.',
    ],
